---
const features = [
  {
    title: "You need clients, not more tools",
    description: "Every new app promises better marketing, but your business still needs clear offers, consistent content, and campaigns that actually move people closer to buying.",
    image: "/images/feature-card-clients-at-door.avif",
  },
  {
    title: "AI keeps changing underneath you",
    description: "Claude gets better, ChatGPT adds features, Gemini expands, and new image models launch. Most teams do not have time to test what is useful and rebuild around it.",
    image: "/images/feature-card-ai-logo-floor.avif",
  },
  {
    title: "Your marketing needs memory",
    description: "A better model still needs your voice, offers, approvals, past campaigns, and what has worked before. Without that context, every campaign starts too close to zero.",
    image: "/images/feature-card-marketing-memory-command.avif",
  },
];
---

<section class="section light-green" id="system-context">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header text-center animate-fade-up">
      <p class="subtitle">THE REAL PROBLEM</p>
      <h2>Every business wants more clients.<br />Most marketing systems are not built to keep up.</h2>
      <p class="section-copy">
        You need marketing that brings in attention, builds trust, and turns interest into real opportunities. But the tools keep changing, the work stays scattered, and the question remains the same: what will actually help the business grow?
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="features-grid animate-stagger">
      {features.map((feature) => (
        <div class="feature-card">
          <div class="feature-card-image">
            <img src={feature.image} alt={feature.title} />
          </div>
          <div class="feature-card-content">
            <h4>{feature.title}</h4>
            <p>{feature.description}</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .section-header {
    margin-bottom: 3.5rem;
  }

  .section-header .subtitle {
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }

  .section-copy {
    margin-top: 1rem;
    max-width: 42rem;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    color: rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.62);
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  .features-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    gap: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-card {
    border: 1px solid var(--neutral-200);
    border-radius: var(--radius-medium);
    overflow: hidden;
    background: transparent;
    transition: border-color 0.4s, transform 0.4s;
  }

  .feature-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(105, 210, 84, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .feature-card-image {
    width: 100%;
    aspect-ratio: 368 / 282;
    overflow: hidden;
  }

  .feature-card-image img {
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    object-fit: cover;
    transition: transform 0.6s ease;
  }

  .feature-card:hover .feature-card-image img {
    transform: scale(1.05);
  }

  .feature-card-content {
    padding: 1.5rem;
  }

  .feature-card-content h4 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .feature-card-content p {
    font-size: 0.875rem;
    color: rgba(15, 18, 19, 0.56);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .features-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      max-width: 400px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }
  }
</style>
